            </div>
            <h3><a href="/blog/independent-educational-evaluation-texas.html">When and How to Request an Independent Educational Evaluation (IEE) in Texas</a></h3>
            <p>If you disagree with the school's evaluation, you may be entitled to an Independent Educational Evaluation at the district's expense. Here's how it works.</p>
            <a class="read-more" href="/blog/independent-educational-evaluation-texas.html">Read more &#8594;</a>
